Package oshi.jna.platform.mac

Provides extensions of JNA libraries for Mac OS X. These classes should be considered non-API as they may be removed if/when their code is incorporated into the JNA project.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CoreFoundation
    CoreFoundation framework for power supply stats.
    DiskArbitration
    DiskArbitration framework for disk stats.
    IOKit
    Power Supply stats.
    SystemB
    System class.
